{{yue-hanzi|jyut=|y=haak3/haa5|tra=嚇}}

# {{defn|lang=yue|sort=口03}}

Grammatical particle used to emphasise an activity which goes on for a brief moment. The usage would be similar to adding ''for a while/moment''. See Mandarin [[一下]]

===Example===
# [[等]][[我]][[諗]][[吓]]。
#: ''dang2 ngo5 nam2 haa5''
#: Let me think about it for a while.
# [[我]][[聽日]][[行]][[吓]]
#: ''ngo5 ting1-jat6 haang4-haa5''
#: Tomorrow, I will take a little walk.

